title: Humane Rat Traps, RatzFatz 2pcs Mouse Traps for Outdoors & Indoor, No Kill, No Harm, Reusable Live Catch Mousetrap, Pet Friendly Rat Catcher, Large 30 cm, Suitable for Mice Squirrel
description: Product Description Do you want to efficiently catch escaping mice or other pests, but don't want to hurt them unnecessarily? With our RatzFatz humane traps, you can efficiently capture animals without hurting or killing them. Our traps are designed to be animal-friendly. The traps are for indoor and outdoor use and they are suitable for most rodents with large space. In addition, no harmful chemicals are used in our traps - Which is unfortunately common practice in most traps. These harmful additives not only harm the captured animals but also your own pets and even humans. Enough space - Suitable for most animals Reusable - An economical way to capture rodents Effective - The anti-escape mechanism ensures effective capture of animals For indoor and outdoor - Suitable for all weather conditions About RatzFatz RatzFatz was developed in Germany and has been working on humane treatment of "troublemakers" or "pests" (such as rats or mice) for many years. Our goal is - to catch animals quickly without harming them. RatzFatz Mouse Trap - Model: "Quick-Catch'' A humane way to capture small animals efficiently without harming them. The innovative anti-escape mechanism ensures that the caught animals will not escape. The specially designed mesh ensures that the caught animals can breathe freely and will not hurt their paws. Suitable for: ＊Mice ＊Small Rats ＊Birds ＊Other animals with similar size Product Size: 13 x 5 x 5 inches (31×13×12cm) Easy to set up Step 1: Pull up the door locking bar to the top, press the "V" shaped bar to hold the door open. (Figure 1) Step 2: Put the bait (cheese, butter, peanut, etc.) onto the hook. (Figure 4) Step 3: Secure the trap with the hook on the top. (Figure 2 and Figure 3) Step 4: Place the trap in areas where rodents often appear.
